{"tid":2293831,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方拘捕一名港鐵職員涉冒警　企圖誘騙女童拍攝裸露短片","createTime":"2020-11-20T13:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T05:48:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8157bacd456cd739966713208fc95267a87e5c00","tid":2293831,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"警方拘捕一名港鐵職員，他涉嫌假冒公職人員，企圖誘騙兩名女童拍攝裸露影片。<br />\n<br />\n被捕的35歲男子夜晚被押解離開西區警署，警方不排除他涉及其他風化案件。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，案中兩名15及16歲的女童，分別是兩宗地鐵案件的事主。她們早前接獲一名男子電話，對方自稱是警員，聲稱協助兩人調查案件，要求兩人傳送自拍的裸露短片。兩名女童報警求助，警方派出探員假扮事主交涉，對方其後要約探員見面，企圖作出不道德行為。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日在長沙灣地鐵站將涉案男子拘捕，並在住所及工作地點檢走一批證物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=413677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D413677&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=eac36ca1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D413677&h=9b0c2635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=413677</a>"},{"pid":"7f60bab30526c5b71fc4469a2a6974346c9ba426","tid":2293831,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e814b375a4b3866e6525099a0889b88204795e","tid":2293831,"uid":21470,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"冇證又冇no , 鳩知係真狗定假狗"},{"pid":"e863876b79d92e82d6c966d202577626228a725b","tid":2293831,"uid":105678,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"罪犯都知要扮黑警，因為兩邊做嘅嘢差唔多但後者唔使負責"},{"pid":"8e40e90f591695ac894267031dec2711bf953548","tid":2293831,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1